Juliet Cesario https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juliet_Cesario 0 Juliet Cesario (born July 14, 1967) is an American actress best known for her voice work in anime, notably You're Under Arrest as Miyuki Kobayakawa, Oh! My Goddess as Belldandy in the OVA series and Peorth in the TV series, and the 2009 release of Clamp School Detectives. Cesario has also appeared in many television series, films and stage productions.
